OL,3,CLegendary West Indies cricketer Sir
OL,4,CGarfield Sobers dies aged 89
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIn a statement on social media,
OL,12,FWindies Cricket said: "A great innings
OL,13,Fhas come to an end.
OL,15,F"In our hearts, now and forever, Sir
OL,16,FGarfield Sobers."
OL,18,FSobers made his debut for Barbados
OL,19,Faged 16 and a year later he was
OL,20,Felevated to West Indies level.
