OL,3,CLegendary West Indies cricketer Sir
OL,4,CGarfield Sobers dies aged 89
OL,6,FThe Board of Control for Cricket in
OL,7,FIndia (BCCI) also paid their respects
OL,8,Fto Sobers on social media.
OL,10,F"His extraordinary achievements,
OL,11,Flasting influence on Caribbean cricket
OL,12,Fand immeasurable contribution to the
OL,13,Fglobal game have left an enduring
OL,14,Flegacy that will continue to inspire
OL,15,Fgenerations," they said.
OL,17,F"Our heartfelt condolences to his
OL,18,Ffamily, friends, and the global
OL,19,Fcricketing fraternity. May his soul
OL,20,Frest in peace."
